The Supplier’s services under this SOW shall commence on 1st September 2025
shall terminate on 1st March 2026 unless otherwise agreed by the parties (“SOW
Term”).

(the “Pilot Project” 31 September 2024 to 31 March 2025) for a fitness and probity
due diligence outsourced solution, whereby the Supplier will be responsible for
conducting the Searches set out in Schedule 1 as part of the Bank’s fitness and
probity regulatory compliance workstream (the “F&P Solution”). This is an
extension of that agreement to the 1st March 2026.

to the Supplier. If additional checks are needed based on the candidate profile,
searches may take up to 10 days to complete. In the event the search will take
longer than 10 days, Supplier will promptly notify the Bank (“SLA”).
